<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قَالَتْ:</span> خَيْرَاً، كَفَّ اللَّهُ يَدَ الفَاجِرِ، وَأخْدَمَ خَادِمَاً<span style="color:#950000">".<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قَالَ أَبُو هُرَيْرَةَ:</span> "فَتِلْكَ أُمُّكُمْ يَا بَنِي مَاءِ السَّمَاءِ".<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هَذَا حَدِيْثٌ صَحِيْحٌ، مُتَّفَقٌ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>***<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>